➜登高望乡当歌《重阳谣》
http://www.sohu.com/a/410782054_100021629	34975
<p><strong>踏莎行过蝶恋花·重阳谣</strong></p>
<p>●文|白润岱 图|张广杰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200731/7f48af9ef3354f0185cade6af0a4311b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>秋满江山，</p>
<p>重阳又到。</p>
<p>离愁浩荡知多少?</p>
<p>远芳引恨望乡人，</p>
<p>棵棵化作断肠草。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200731/ccc7470ad66e4a9e81c825520a46a2a2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>归路迢迢，</p>
<p>流云袅袅。</p>
<p>云霞激荡天光皎，</p>
<p>伤心最是月如刀，</p>
<p>刀刀摧瘦菊花老。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200731/fcc656e874a34573b54804ba79751c43.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>秋讯年年何日了?</p>
<p>游子轻狂，</p>
<p>把酒回一笑。</p>
<p>自古人狂心寂寥，</p>
<p>重阳愁重嫌杯小。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200731/91ff4560622148e0b381a4fdc95dee57.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>莫叹红尘缘缈缈，</p>
<p>但举觥筹，</p>
<p>遥祝亲人好。</p>
<p>愿向苍天赊亿岁，</p>
<p>豪情陪送青山老。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200731/6dfa3f92e347414a977c435f94babc4d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>( 2020年7月31日就)</p>